articles.author: Guardian staff reporter
articles.title: Lisa Marie Presley died from weight-loss surgery complications, autopsy finds - The Guardian
articles.description: January death of Elvis Presley’s daughter, 54, ruled as being from natural causes due to effects of small bowel obstruction
articles.content:
Lisa Marie Presley died from complications from bariatric surgery she had several years ago, authorities have said.
